        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> A very well thought out, and worded post!   I agree with your rankings as stated (as a level 54 necro)</P><P>You are way too analytical for your own good  :)</P><P>what verant will do is the question (if anything)    They have 2 main problems:</P><P>1: they will probably screw it up due to the complexity of the issue and the fact that they make a lot of errors in coding and<BR>judgement. ...even if it works OK on a blue server, thoses of us on PVP servers will have to endure till they fix it again (happens every time)</P><P>2:  Regardless of what and how they implement the changes, people will complain on the blue servers and the PVP servers so much they will not really have an idea of what needs to be modified for a while.</P><P>It will be a win/loose situation for a while till they balance things out and we can only hope they get it right.....bear in mind they are still balancing classes after over 3 years.....but it is in no way easy to do and I do not envy them one bit.</P><P>Kwisan</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
